      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "首先建立隔离的 WorkTree 进行子功能需求的开发：\n\n# nanoclaw-v2\ncd ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork/nanoclaw-v2\ngit worktree add ../nanoclaw-v2-stage3 -b stage3-multi-platform-content\n\n# nanoclaw-dashboard-v2（另一个 repo·直接开 branch 或 worktree）\ncd ~/projects/nanoclaw-dashboard-v2\ngit worktree add ../nanoclaw-dashboard-v2-stage3 -b stage3-multi-platform-content\n\n\n两个 worktree 目录：\n\n- `~/projects/nanoclaw-fork/nanoclaw-v2-stage3`——后端（Sub-1/3 的代码）\n- `~/projects/nanoclaw-dashboard-v2-stage3`——前端（Sub-4 的代码）\n",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "lHX-xq6gPrsMfXcdFpwKp",
      "originalText": "首先建立隔离的 WorkTree 进行子功能需求的开发：\n\n# nanoclaw-v2\ncd ~/projects/nanoclaw-fork/nanoclaw-v2\ngit worktree add ../nanoclaw-v2-stage3 -b stage3-multi-platform-content\n\n# nanoclaw-dashboard-v2（另一个 repo·直接开 branch 或 worktree）\ncd ~/projects/nanoclaw-dashboard-v2\ngit worktree add ../nanoclaw-dashboard-v2-stage3 -b stage3-multi-platform-content\n\n\n两个 worktree 目录：\n\n- `~/projects/nanoclaw-fork/nanoclaw-v2-stage3`——后端（Sub-1/3 的代码）\n- `~/projects/nanoclaw-dashboard-v2-stage3`——前端（Sub-4 的代码）\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
